<plot>Morgan, a socially inept mortician, is continually late to work due to traffic. Jim, the mortuary owner repeatedly grills Morgan for his tardiness. Morgan discovers a twisted way for prompt arrival: using the dead people from the mortuary to legally drive in the carpool lane. He is only able to keep his genius idea a secret for so long.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?552329</url></doc>
